Wal-Mart Will Expand City by City in African Markets, Financial Times Says

-- B y   J o h n   S i m p s o n
-- 
2011-06-05T23:21:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-05/wal-mart-to-expand-city-by-city-in-african-markets-ft-reports.html
Wal-Mart Stores Inc. (WMT)  plans to expand
across Africa city by city, rather than country by country, and
will apply “sweat and muscle” in its distribution, compared
with the high technology it employs in the U.S., the Financial
Times reported, citing Doug McMillon, chief executive officer of
Wal-Mart International.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Simpson at 
 jsimpson12@bloomberg.net  